songs.title: Law

Cause I slay everyday, and I do this shit for fun

Any bitch that ever hated on you, know you got that sauce
Say you on your healthy shit, you got a salad saving sauce
And I ain’t met another chick yet, that can top me
I flex on these bitches time after time, Cyndi Lauper
A nigga gotta keep me in exclusives I’m a shopper
And if I can’t have it my way I’ma spazz and re-rob her
I pull up in a Mazzi just to drop off a deposit
Money ain’t everything to a nigga who ain’t got it
Cut it, bag it, stuff it, ship it, break it down and lock it
By any means if I want it, then daddy he better cop it
The people fucking with me, you can tell I got them bars
I mean, you see these fucking diamonds you can tell that I’m a star
Got triple zeros interlocked, is the emblem on my car
I kill these bitches then give ‘em they life, CPR
